    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey my left eye is super red and it kind of hurts a bit. also there's this yellowish stuff coming out of it when i wake up. i probably just have really dry eyes from being on my laptop all day for work. do u think i should just get some lubricating eye drops from the pharmacy to make it better?",
