      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait antibiotic ointment?? i can't really go to the clinic right now, i'm super busy with work and it's kinda expensive to see a specialist. isn't it basically the same thing as using regular eye drops for a few days? like, can i just try some drops first and if it doesn't work in a week i'll deal with it then?",
